title: [Stone Baths, Nexus]
description: The dimly lit hallway opens up into a wide spherical chamber with a smooth, dark slate floor.  Maoral-framed paintings enhance the russet-hued walls, and arched windows provide a profusion of silvery moonlight.  Ceramic pots of white gardenia rest between a silver arch and a brass arch.  Spaced evenly around the room are number of different doors.
